          Documentation panel  443\u00D7310 4.29 KB         \n To delete an element, select and remove the entire line. \n When you\u2019re finished, don\u2019t forget to save your changes. \nThe documentation editor has its own save button that must be used: \n          Save icon in Documentation  341\u00D7141 2.34 KB         \n   Client Application \n Here are some examples showing how documentation elements appear in the client application. \n Tooltip: \n  \n Workflow step: \n         USER_WFSTEP_DESCRIPTION example 1  433\u00D7194 16.4 KB         \n         USER_WFSTEP_DESCRIPTION example 2  543\u00D7182 15.4 KB         \n   Other topics \n   Source file \n The content of your documentation elements is stored in an XML file located at: \n your_project/model/package/.origamDoc  file \n   Translations \n Documentation texts are part of the localization file and are exported along with screen labels and other elements. \n If you need to translate any of the documentation elements, add their names to the  OrigamSettings.config  file: \n         Connection Configuration Properties  425\u00D7204 4.48 KB","vector_provider":"AI.Ollama.OllamaTextEmbeddingGenerator","vector_generator":"__","last_update":"2026-04-29T00:23:22"},"vector":[0.0035216059,-0.022845129,-0.06499308,0.0069419253,0.0010155314,-0.052083213,0.012192595,-0.023021804,-0.0072190985,-0.007827194,0.0041950466,0.0104442965,0.025438063,-0.024667786,-0.014674036,-0.013092184,-0.0037410322,0.00048949424,0.044132993,-0.00071808876,0.018923819,0.01852059,0.042257898,0.0072856024,0.030907542,0.018062696,-0.034544643,-0.024684034,0.042616382,0.01249917,-0.0030780362,-0.04721552,-0.00884078,-0.0026263273,-0.019642627,0.025977375,0.028331876,0.0313838,-0.041209828,0.022691445,0.0066691902,-0.02041023,-0.0026081253,0.009523369,0.01237147,-0.047103856,-0.022587249,-0.0035565512,0.014627762,-0.033691138,-0.037943326,-0.015023821,0.019453129,-0.07470706,0.019096015,0.05246301,-0.052575212,-0.029397639,-0.06045176,0.0444